<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.7">
<l>mālaip pukuntu malaraṇaimēl vaiki yaṭiyēṉ maṉampukunteṉ</l>
<l>nīlak kaṇkaḷ paṉimalka niṉṟār niṉṟa vūrpōlum</l>
<l>vēlaik kaṭalpōl neṭuvīti viṇtōy cutaiveṇ maṇimāṭat</l>
<l>tālaip pukaiyā laḻalkatirai maṟaikkum vīti yaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city where stands the one who, having come at dusk to me, his servant,</l>
<l rend="indent">lingering on a flowery bed,</l>
<l>And entering my mind, stayed when tears gathered in my dark eyes,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr with streets where fires hide the sun with smoke</l>
<l rend="indent">which billows</l>
<l>From a white plastered, beautiful, raised shrine which touches the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">on a street, wide like the seashore.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
